---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="ui-new-footer">
  <div class="ui-new-footer-inner">
    <div class="ui-new-footer-copy">
      <span class="ui-new-footer-year">© {year}</span>
      <span class="ui-new-footer-name">摸鱼热榜</span>
    </div>

    <div class="ui-new-footer-disclaimer">
      <p>本站仅聚合公开榜单标题与原站链接，点击后跳转至原网站。</p>
      <p>内容版权归原平台及原作者所有。</p>
      <p>市场行情数据仅供信息展示，不构成投资建议。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ui-new-footer-meta">
      <span>BUILT WITH ASTRO · FASTAPI</span>
      <span class="ui-new-footer-dot">·</span>
      <span>NO COOKIES · NO TRACKING</span>
      <span class="ui-new-footer-dot">·</span>
      <span>OPEN SOURCE</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .ui-new-footer {
    margin-top: 34px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border, #eaeaea);
    background: var(--background, #ffffff);
    color: var(--text-secondary, #525252);
  }

  .ui-new-footer-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(220px, 1fr) auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 22px 24px 30px;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-copy {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    min-width: max-content;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-year {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border, #eaeaea);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 6px);
    background: var(--surface-elevated, #ffffff);
    color: var(--text-primary, #171717);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 650;
    padding: 0 8px;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-name {
    color: var(--text-primary, #171717);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-disclaimer {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary, #525252);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-disclaimer p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary, #8f8f8f);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .ui-new-footer-dot {
    opacity: 0.52;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .ui-new-footer-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .ui-new-footer-meta {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .ui-new-footer-inner {
      padding: 20px 16px 26px;
    }
  }
</style>
